comments: Covington (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Monk (LAL) and does not deliver contact.
Powell (POR) reaches in and makes contact with Davis' (LAL) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Monk (LAL) makes marginal contact with McCollum's (POR) arm after the release of his shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Nurkic (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful as Nurkic turns his body to the side and initiates contact with Davis (LAL) while contesting the play at the basket.
Bradley (LAL) reaches in and makes contact to the front of Simons' (POR) body during his drive.
Covington (POR) commits a take foul on Anthony (LAL).
Covington (POR) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
Powell (POR) commits a take foul on Monk (LAL).
Davis (LAL) extends his lower body into McCollum's (POR) body and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Simons (POR) commits a take foul on Monk (LAL).
